)Body window(65,05)
%Command ===>_zcmd
%
%CSD name   ===>|csdname                                    +
%CSD Object ===>|object  |otype+G(roup) L(ist)+
%Generation ===>|g+            +B(atch) O(nline)+
)INIT
 .CURSOR = object
 &zwinttl= 'CICS CSD commands'
)REINIT
 REFRESH(*)
)PROC
   VER (&csdname,NB,msg=cica001)
   VER (&object,NB,msg=cica001)
   VER (&g,NB,msg=cica001)
)END

$ / /  CICS CSD Connection summary / /
%Command ===>_zcmd                                 / /%Scroll ===>_amt +
%
%Command      :@select%information
%selection ==>:¬sel
%line commands:$s%;dynp0,shdp0                ;
%
$                         ACC  Single    Auto    In      Attach    Bind   Dflt
$  Conn Group    Netname  meth session connect Service secururity secur.  user
%/=/=/=/
)Model
|a#conn#group   #netname #acme#sin    #auto   +   #ins#attsec    +  #bis+ #dfu+
)Init
 &amt           = CSR
 .ATTR(sel)     = 'color(turq) HILITE(REVERSE)'
 .attr(conn)    = 'color(blue)'
 .attr(group)   = 'color(turq)'
 .attr(netname) = 'color(turq)'
 .attr(acme)    = 'color(turq)'
 .attr(sin)     = 'color(pink)'
 .attr(auto)    = 'color(red)'
 .attr(attsec)  = 'color(red) just(right)'
 .attr(ins)     = 'color(red)'
 .attr(bis)     = 'color(yellow) just(right)'
 .attr(dfu)     = 'color(yellow) just(right)'
  &dynp0        = '= display sessions'
  &shdp0        = '          ?'
)Reinit
)Proc
  VPUT (ZTDTOP)
)PNTS
FIELD(ZPS00001) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(SELECT)
)End

$ / /  CICS CSD Profile summary / /
%Command ===>_zcmd                                 / /%Scroll ===>_amt +
%
%Command      :@select%information
%selection ==>:¬sel
%line commands:$t%;dynp0,shdp0                           ;
%
$  Profile  Group    Scrnsize  Uctran inbfmh
%/=/=/=/
)Model
|a#prof    #group   #scrnsize #uctran#inbfmh+
)Init
 &amt = CSR
 .ATTR(sel)     = 'color(turq) HILITE(REVERSE)'
 .attr(prof)    = 'color(blue)'
 .attr(group)   = 'color(turq)'
 .attr(scrnsize)= 'color(pink)'
 .attr(uctran)  = 'color(yellow)'
 .attr(inbfmh ) = 'color(red)'
  &dynp0        = '= select transactions with profile'
  &shdp0        = '         ?'
)Reinit
)Proc
  VPUT (ZTDTOP)
)PNTS
FIELD(ZPS00001) VAR(ZCMD) VAL(SELECT)
)End
